 to \"quantum\"\nramified D-modules and Lagrangian intersection Floer homology; (ii) furnish\nphysical proofs of mathematical conjectures by Seidel-Smith [2] and Gaitsgory\n[3, 4] which relate knots to symplectic geometry and Langlands duality,\nrespectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2011 23:42:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Aug 2013 16:48:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2013 12:21:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-03"}
