ndom f with Binomial distribution the expected gap remains\nO(log(n)/beta) independent of the total number of balls thrown. This is the\nfirst such tight result for (1 +beta) paradigm with multidimensional balls and\nbins.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2011 09:14:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2011 09:59:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-11-30"}
